column5: ACUPUNCTURE FOR MALE HEALTH CONCERNShttp://www.acupunctureformenshealth.com show contact infoThe practitioners with Acupuncture For Men's Health are specialists in male health concerns. Erectile Dysfunction Premature Ejaculation  Inhibited Ejaculation Low & High Libido Frequent, Hesitant, Urgent Urination Prostatitis Hernia Groin pain Hemorrhoids Hair loss Diabetes High blood pressure Cholesterol Insomnia Sore joints and muscles Weight Loss, Gas, BloatingGoutArthritisInjuries.... and other general health related concerns. Treatments are relaxing and informative, personable and professional. Needles are placed in legs, feet, arms and back, and DO NOT HURT, you might even take a nice relaxing nap. Note: We do not need to place needles directly in the genitals when treated for sexual health concerns. Call  show contact info to talk to an acupuncturist for information and scheduling. show contact infoTreatments are confidential and private. Does your insurance plan cover acupuncture? Tuina and Shiatsu massage also available by some practitioners along with acupuncture treatments.

I'm noticing a level of a deeper and quite thorough inner completeness; an unusual degree of a thorough contentment. I've done a lot of mindfulness work over the years, and so I believe I am pretty sensitive to my emotional & subtler aspects of my experiences."Book your cuddle session with me at http://cuddlist.com/nancyjo/ for $80/hr. Give yourself the amazing gift of transformative touch through cuddling.

column5: Give yourself the gift of connection and healing touch through Cuddling!My name is Nancy Jo and I am a Certified Professional Cuddler through Cuddlist.com. I provide a strictly non-sexual service based on mutual respect. Because cuddling is based on clear consent and communication, it is a safe way to explore your needs and wants. Recent Cuddlist.com Testimonial:"The level of a deep calm that I'm experiencing is very, very special!  I feel like I've had some parts of me either healed or touched, held and celebrated!  I'm noticing a level of a deeper and quite thorough inner completeness; an unusual degree of a thorough contentment.  I do not say these things to be nice to you, or even as a way of saying "a heart-felt thank you".  Rather, it's this very peaceful place that I am experiencing from.  I've done a lot of mindfulness work over the years, and so I believe I am pretty sensitive to my emotional & subtler aspects of my experiences."Book your cuddle session with me at http://cuddlist.com/nancyjo/ for $80/hr. Give yourself the amazing gift of transformative touch through cuddling.

I provide a strictly non-sexual service based on mutual respect. Because cuddling is based on clear consent and communication, it is a safe way to explore your needs and wants. Recent Cuddlist.com Testimonial:"The level of a deep calm that I'm experiencing is very, very special!  I feel like I've had some parts of me either healed or touched, held and celebrated!  I'm noticing a level of a deeper and quite thorough inner completeness; an unusual degree of a thorough contentment.  I do not say these things to be nice to you, or even as a way of saying "a heart-felt thank you".  Rather, it's this very peaceful place that I am experiencing from.  I've done a lot of mindfulness work over the years, and so I believe I am pretty sensitive to my emotional & subtler aspects of my experiences."Book your cuddle session with me at http://cuddlist.com/nancyjo/ for $80/hr. Give yourself the amazing gift of transformative touch through cuddling.

I provide a strictly non-sexual service based on mutual respect. Because cuddling is based on clear consent and communication, it is a safe way to explore your needs and wants. Recent Cuddlist.com Testimonial:"The level of a deep calm that I'm experiencing is very, very special!  I feel like I've had some parts of me either healed or touched, held and celebrated!  I'm noticing a level of a deeper and quite thorough inner completeness; an unusual degree of a thorough contentment.  I do not say these things to be nice to you, or even as a way of saying "a heart-felt thank you".  Rather, it's this very peaceful place that I am experiencing from.  I've done a lot of mindfulness work over the years, and so I believe I am pretty sensitive to my emotional & subtler aspects of my experiences."Book your cuddle session with me at http://cuddlist.com/nancyjo/ for $80/hr. Give yourself the amazing gift of transformative touch through cuddling.

column5: I am a world-class male massage therapist born in Japan and living in the United States for the past 25 years. I am skilled in numerous techniques and therapies, including Shiatsu, Swedish, Neuromuscular, Myoskeletal Alignment, Trigger Point, Thai Stretching and Sports Massage, as well as spa body-scrub treatments (shower available). column5: ACUPUNCTURE FOR MALE HEALTH CONCERNShttp://www.acupunctureformenshealth.com show contact infoThe practitioners with Acupuncture For Men's Health are specialists in male health concerns. Erectile Dysfunction Premature Ejaculation  Inhibited Ejaculation Low & High Libido Frequent, Hesitant, Urgent Urination Prostatitis Hernia Groin pain Hemorrhoids Hair loss Diabetes High blood pressure Cholesterol Insomnia Sore joints and muscles Weight Loss, Gas, BloatingGoutArthritisInjuries.... and other general health related concerns. Treatments are relaxing and informative, personable and professional. Needles are placed in legs, feet, arms and back, and DO NOT HURT, you might even take a nice relaxing nap. Note: We do not need to place needles directly in the genitals when treated for sexual health concerns. Call  show contact info to talk to an acupuncturist for information and scheduling. show contact infoTreatments are confidential and private. Does your insurance plan cover acupuncture? Tuina and Shiatsu massage also available by some practitioners along with acupuncture treatments.

column5: I am a world-class male massage therapist born in Japan and living in the United States for the past 25 years. I am skilled in numerous techniques and therapies, including Shiatsu, Swedish, Neuromuscular, Myoskeletal Alignment, Trigger Point, Thai Stretching and Sports Massage, as well as spa body-scrub treatments (shower available). I am located just inside the perimeter less than a mile from I-285 and Chamblee-Dunwoody.PRICESMassage (Swedish, Relaxation, Light Massage)* 1-hour massage: $70* 90-minute massage: $100Massage + Spa Treatment (Body Scrub, Seaweed Wrap, Mud Wrap, Aroma Therapy Wrap)* 1-hour massage + 30-minute spa treatment: $110* 90-minute massage + 20-minute spa treatment: $140Specialty Massages (Shiatsu, Deep Tissue, Neuromuscular, Sports, Thai Stretching, Maternity/Pregnancy Massage)* 1-hour specialty massage: $75* 90-minute sports massage: $110Foot Massage (Reflexology)* 30-minute foot massage: $40* 1-hour foot massage: $70Quick Service* 40-minute massage + 20-minute spa treatment: $100All massage/treatment appointments include hot-towel service and small bottle of water. Shower available.Hours:Monday - Friday 10 am - 6 pm (last appointment starts at 5)Saturday 10 am - 7 pm (last appointment starts at 6)Sunday closed (special appointments can be made with advance notice)Weekday and Saturday appointments fill early, so whenever possible, please book 24 hours in advance or at least by early morning for a same-day session.Get relaxed and rejuvenate yourself! I've done a lot of mindfulness work over the years, and so I believe I am pretty sensitive to my emotional & subtler aspects of my experiences."Book your cuddle session with me at http://cuddlist.com/nancyjo/ for $80/hr. column5: Give yourself the gift of connection and healing touch through Cuddling!My name is Nancy Jo and I am a Certified Professional Cuddler through Cuddlist.com. I provide a strictly non-sexual service based on mutual respect. Because cuddling is based on clear consent and communication, it is a safe way to explore your needs and wants. Recent Cuddlist.com Testimonial:"The level of a deep calm that I'm experiencing is very, very special!  I feel like I've had some parts of me either healed or touched, held and celebrated!  I'm noticing a level of a deeper and quite thorough inner completeness; an unusual degree of a thorough contentment.  I do not say these things to be nice to you, or even as a way of saying "a heart-felt thank you".  Rather, it's this very peaceful place that I am experiencing from.  I've done a lot of mindfulness work over the years, and so I believe I am pretty sensitive to my emotional & subtler aspects of my experiences."Book your cuddle session with me at http://cuddlist.com/nancyjo/ for $80/hr. Give yourself the amazing gift of transformative touch through cuddling.

column5: Hi come and enjoy a Shiatsu/Deep Tissue/Thia stretching or a relaxing Swedish full body massage at my private Massage room,I can travel and bring my massage table. My place is $65 for the hour and $35extra to travel. Strong massage extra $10Ask me about my 90min rates/ Free hot stone massageTallahassee massage salon929 north monroe stCall or text  show contact info MartinI have a certificate & diploma in remedial / relaxation massage together with hundreds of hours experience along with a strong body and good hands to deliver the perfect massage.The massage can be very specific to particular areas of the body or it can be more globally focused on the entire body. The massage is a healing treatment for tense, tight and even knotted muscles. The healing comes via the way the massage is performed, either gently or strong and the depth and pressure used on the body tissue. If you would like your massage to be targeted to specific body areas to free up tight and/or sore muscles, I will tailor massage techniques to your needs, so you get the results you are after. I am a highly experienced and intuitive massage therapist, I bring a relaxed atmosphere to all my massages and my goal is to let my clients unwind and relieve any built up physical tension and associated stresses.Benefits of MassageIf you are experiencing:Back painHeadachesAching jointsTight musclesPostural problemsNeck painThe massage treatment is ideal to assist with any of these problem areas. Massage therapy is also good for people who are under stress, active people coping with injury and strains during their rehab process or professional athletes just wanting to maintain an edge. The massage treatment is also ideal for tradespeople who generally put their bodies under a lot of manual stress on a daily and ongoing basis.tallahassee massage spa 929 north monroe stopen 9am to 9pm 7 day a week and walk-ins welcome or make appointment call or text  show contact info martin

column5: I have been a certified massage therapist for over 10 years, and love my work. I am new to the area and excited to continue my work, and share my gift of massage. I am willing to work with you on pricing depending on how close you are to me.  show contact info. My preferred method of communication is texting, but feel free to call anytime. I mainly work doing out-call, which means I will come to you. I can arrange in-call if that works better for you.
